Mukherjee Sees Indian Economic Growth Picking Up in Second Half

-- B y   P r a d e e p   K u r u p
-- 
2011-09-16T10:51:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/mukherjee-sees-indian-economic-growth-picking-up-in-second-half.html
The Reserve Bank of  India ’s
decision today to raise interest rates by 25 basis points leaves
scope for economic growth to pick up in the second half of the
year, Finance Minister  Pranab Mukherjee  said in an e-mailed
statement today.  The central bank’s policy will help the country get back to
a more “comfortable inflation situation,” Mukherjee said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Pradeep Kurup at 
 pkurup3@bloomberg.net  